dct_description_sm: Ioannes a Deutecu, Lucas a Deutecu, fecerunt.
Bar scale on map given in "Scala miliaria Ger. conti."
Decorative border and cartouches, pictorial vignettes with figures and animals, ships, sea monsters.
From De Jode's Speculum orbis terrarum, Antwerp, first published in 1578, reissued by Cornelis in 1593.
